This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a meta-learning approach to learn task-specific feature embeddings. The paper also deals with image classification tasks, which suggests that it could belong to computer vision (cs.CV) as well. Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which could place it in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
